type="user">jms-00MH</fr:addr><fr:route>jms-00MH.xml</fr:route><fr:title
text="Countable set">Countable set</fr:title><fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>A <fr:em><fr:strong>countable set</fr:strong></fr:em> is one that is either empty or <fr:link
href="jms-00ME.xml"
title="Enumerable set"
addr="jms-00ME"
type="local">enumerable</fr:link>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:tree
show-metadata="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
href="jonmsterling.xml"
title="Jon Sterling"
addr="jonmsterling"
type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>29</fr:day></fr:date><fr:anchor>6903</fr:anchor><fr:addr
type="user">jms-00MI</fr:addr><fr:route>jms-00MI.xml</fr:route><fr:title
text="Alternative definition of countability">Alternative definition of <fr:link
href="jms-00MH.xml"
title="Countable set"
addr="jms-00MH"
type="local">countability</fr:link></fr:title><fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>A set <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="jms-00MH.xml"
title="Countable set"
addr="jms-00MH"
type="local">countable</fr:link> if and only if the disjoint union <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="jms-00ME.xml"
title="Enumerable set"
addr="jms-00ME"
type="local">enumerable</fr:link>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
show-metadata="false"
toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
href="jonmsterling.xml"
title="Jon Sterling"
addr="jonmsterling"
type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2024</fr:year><fr:month>1</fr:month><fr:day>29</fr:day></fr:date><fr:anchor>6902</fr:anchor><fr:addr
type="machine">unstable/6047</fr:addr><fr:route>unstable-6047.xml</fr:route><fr:title
text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>Suppose that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="jms-00MH.xml"
title="Countable set"
addr="jms-00MH"
type="local">countable</fr:link>. We must find a <fr:link
href="jms-00M8.xml"
title="Surjection"
addr="jms-00M8"
type="local">surjection</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow  A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>; if <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is empty, this is the same as to find a <fr:link
href="jms-00M8.xml"
title="Surjection"
addr="jms-00M8"
type="local">surjection</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {N}\to {\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>, which we have by <fr:link
href="jms-00MA.xml"
title="Non-empty sets and surjections"
addr="jms-00MA"
type="local">Example <fr:contextual-number
addr="jms-00MA" /></fr:link>. On the other hand, if we have an enumeration <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[e\colon \mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow {A}]]></fr:tex>, we may define an enumeration <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[e'\colon \mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow  A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> as follows:</fr:p>
 <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[
  \begin {aligned}
  e'{\mathopen {}\left (0\right )\mathclose {}} &= 0\\
  e'{\mathopen {}\left (n+1\right )\mathclose {}} &= e{\mathopen {}\left (n\right )\mathclose {}}
  \end {aligned}
 ]]></fr:tex>

 <fr:p>Conversely, suppose that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="jms-00ME.xml"
title="Enumerable set"
addr="jms-00ME"
type="local">enumerable</fr:link> by <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[e\colon \mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow  A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex>. If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is empty, we are done. If to the contrary <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is inhabited by some <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a_0]]></fr:tex>, we let define <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[e'\colon  \mathbb {N}\twoheadrightarrow  A]]></fr:tex> as follows:</fr:p>
 <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[
  e'{\mathopen {}\left (i\right )\mathclose {}} =
  \begin {cases}
   e{\mathopen {}\left (i\right )\mathclose {}} &\text {when } e{\mathopen {}\left (i\right )\mathclose {}}\in  A\\
   a_0 &\text {otherwise}
  \end {cases}
 ]]></fr:tex>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:tree
